<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Full Stack Encryption - Demo 03</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>The server sent the ciphertext encoded in Base64</p>
    <p id="base64"><%= data %></p>
    <p><span id="open-form">Click me</span> to decrypt.</p>
    <p id="plaintext"></p>
    <form action="#" id="private-key-form">
      <p>Paste your private key here. It's in the main directory of the repository: <i>private_key.pem</i></p>
      <textarea id="private-key"></textarea>
      <br>
      <input id="decrypt" type="submit" value="Decrypt!">
    </form>
    <script src="/static/script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
